headline: Ross Dress for Less Opens at First National Realty Partners' Crossroads South in Georgia
summary: First National Realty Partners (FNRP), a leading national private equity commercial real estate firm, announced the opening of Ross Dress for Less at Crossroads South shopping center in Jonesboro, Georgia. The national off-price retailer has opened a 22,000-square-foot anchor store, strengthening the center's tenant mix and increasing its overall appeal to shoppers.
